  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/d090bea530c04330a4a701f0494517b5.avif?t=1725286453\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>This time around, Chess Dungeons is set in beautiful japanese landscapes! <br>Enjoy 360-degree control over the board to not only visualize the beautiful scenery and character models, <br>but also choose your preferred method of playing the game!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/fe50900d4fc482eddca521943f2c8381.avif?t=1725286453\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><i>Some puzzles have a larger number of pieces than traditional chess.</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/4a5b4513948c1c8dcb330bf3f0792fcc.poster.avif?t=1725286453\" width=528 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/4a5b4513948c1c8dcb330bf3f0792fcc.webm?t=1725286453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/4a5b4513948c1c8dcb330bf3f0792fcc.mp4?t=1725286453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/f0bb258b2eaf1cb86cb471a0bb0c1798.avif?t=1725286453\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/ac6372a6ce0e9c5fa2adeb51eb1bc3c4.avif?t=1725286453\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>In this game mode, only one thing matters: slay your opponent's King. <br>You can still attack other pieces, but success is only achieved by knocking out the enemy King.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/1289923519da59f8372915ae9f2fa285.poster.avif?t=1725286453\" width=516 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/1289923519da59f8372915ae9f2fa285.webm?t=1725286453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/1289923519da59f8372915ae9f2fa285.mp4?t=1725286453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/66a8830e192e441407621157b555e674.avif?t=1725286453\" width=600 height=100 /></span><br>Instead of slaying the king, this time you have to wipe out all enemy pieces! <br>Pawns, rooks, bishops, knights, queens and kings all should be eliminated!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/96676846142803203ffc2cc01ebb1cf5.poster.avif?t=1725286453\" width=516 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/96676846142803203ffc2cc01ebb1cf5.webm?t=1725286453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2118010/extras/96676846142803203ffc2cc01ebb1cf5.mp4?t=1725286453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
